dmca.title: [ABUSE] Notification of Infringement
dmca.body:
To Whom It May Concern:

 

Please note that our customer has represented to us that the content
referenced in your Trademark notice (attached below) has been removed
and/or disabled.

 

Legal Response Team

The Planet

 
 
Subject: [ABUSE] Notification of Infringement
Date: Mon, 19 Jun 2006 18:03:33 -0400 (EDT)
From: Legal@Primerica.com
To: sales@instantbizempires.com
CC: admins@theplanet.com, abuse@theplanet.com



PRIMERICA



A member of *citigroup*




Office of the General Counsel

3120 Breckinridge Boulevard

Duluth, Georgia 30099-0001

(770) 381-1000





06/19/2006



*TO: sales@instantbizempires.com*

**

*RE: 1.1.171*

* http://www.top-life-insurance-resource.info/*

**

Dear Joel Teo:



It has recently come to our attention that your website, located at
_http://www.top-life-insurance-resource.info/_was produced in search
results on several keywords related to Primerica, a wholly-owned
subsidiary of Citigroup. A review of your website shows that Primerica's
mark is included in the Metatag


- --
Thanks,

Policy Enforcement
The Planet Internet Services, Inc.
http://www.theplanet.com/legal/aup.html
